Enum TalkerId

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<TalkerId>
      net.sf.marineapi.nmea.sentence.TalkerId
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TalkerId>
public enum TalkerId
extends java.lang.Enum<TalkerId>

Talker defines the supported NMEA Talker IDs. Talker ID is the first two characters in the address field, e.g. "GP" in "$GPGGA". *

Version:
$Revision: 13 $
Author:
Kimmo Tuukkanen
